Following our meeting about the integration of the AI anomaly detection tool into our infrastructure, I've started compiling a list of considerations to ensure we align with the 2025 Cyber Security Cooperation Program and our deadline of Q3 2026.

I'd appreciate it if each department could contribute their expertise to this list.

Best,
Jordan", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Re: Initial Thoughts on AI Anomaly Detection Integration", "from": "michael.roberts@mediconnsolutions.com", "from_name": "Michael Roberts", "to": ["jordan.lee@mediconnsolutions.com", "emily.hayes@mediconnsolutions.com", "david.walker@mediconnsolutions.com", "sarah.johnson@mediconnsolutions.com", "laura.jones@mediconnsolutions.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2026-01-12 11:45:00", "body": "Jordan and Team,

